public class GuiSwingViewCollectionTable extends Object implements GuiSwingView
a swing view for GuiReprCollectionTable

swing-value

GuiSwingViewCollectionTable.CollectionTable.getSwingViewValue(): latest set List.

history-value

Currently unsupported.

string-transfer

entire copying is supported by owned GuiSwingViewPropertyPane.PropertyPane. the entire copying is handled by GuiRepresentation.toHumanReadableString(GuiMappingContext, Object) -> GuiReprObjectPane.toHumanReadableStringFromObject(GuiMappingContext, Object) -> GuiRepresentation.toHumanReadableString(GuiMappingContext, Object).

selected rows or cells can be achieved by ToStringCopyCell based on TableTargetCellAction.
